Package skynail.domain

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Point
    Interface for map points.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    City
    Map point for cities, presently unfinished.
    Companion
    Companions are specialised Game Characters that are part of player parties.
    Dungeon
    Map point containing a monster and treasure, currently partially unfinished.
    GameCharacter
    Basic class for characters containing game logic for battle scenes.
    Item
    Consumable items that can be used in combat.
    Monster
    Monsters are specialised GameCharacters present in dungeons.
    Player
    Class for storing a player's characters and other statistics.
    Road
    Simple map point.
    Trophy
    The trophy stores the rewards received from exploring a dungeon.
